At about 3 p.m. the police arrived at the █████ house and asked ██████ ██████ whether her husband owned a rifle. She said that he did and then led them into the garage and pointed to the rolled up blanket. As a police officer lifted it, the blanket hung limply over either side of his arm. The rifle was not there.

